Zapyle rests on a strong policy of authenticity. All the products listed on Zapyle are 100% authentic.We only approve products with high quality images and which feature in our list of 550 brands.

Our trained in-house professionals, including apparel experts and handbag appraisers ensure that every item sold and bought on our platform is 100% authentic and in great condition, preloved or brand new.

A trained team of luxury experts passes every item to be bought or sold through a second round of authentication process where they are checked on a multi-point system, before they are accepted for listing.
Each item is inspected for original brand logos, date codes, serial tags and hologram stickers before it is curated into daily sales.
Our goal at Zapyle is to provide you a luxury experience, so rest assured and shop stress free.
